Folder Structure 

Parent Folder 
│
├── app.py                      # Main Python backend file handling routes and logic
├── attendance.csv               # File storing attendance data in CSV format
├── students_images/             # Folder containing images of students for face recognition
│
├── static/                      # Folder for static frontend assets (CSS, JavaScript)
│   ├── css/                     # Contains stylesheets
│   │   └── styles.css           # CSS for your web pages
│   └── js/                      # Contains JavaScript files for frontend interactivity
│       └── script.js            # Any client-side JavaScript logic
│
├── templates/                   # Folder containing HTML templates for various web pages
│   ├── ams_panel.html           # Attendance Management System panel page
│   ├── capture_attendance.html  # Page for capturing attendance via camera
│   ├── dashboard.html           # Dashboard page for viewing summary information
│   ├── login.html               # Login page for teachers or admins
│   ├── signup.html              # Signup page for new users
│
└── uploads/                     # Folder storing uploaded images


To Run : python app.py
